# Object Detection and Tracking (YOLO + SORT)

## Description

This project performs real-time object detection using YOLOv8 and tracks objects using SORT.

## Features

- Auto detection (YOLO built-in)
- Manual detection (custom bounding boxes)
- Class filtering (person)
- Object tracking with IDs

## Requirements

pip install -r requirements.txt

## Run

python main.py
